entries.complete: Contract fulfilled! The Gotal have learned some respect!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_2: You've made the worst mistake of your life!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_3: You may have defeated my men... but you won't defeat me!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_4: Just close your eyes. I promise to make it quick.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_5: Let's see if you put up a better fight than the last one did!
entries.found_loc: Intercept coordinates found! Proceed with caution.
entries.level_boss: They have dispatched a %TO to bring you down! Be careful!
entries.level_boss_dead: The enemy commander has been destroyed!
entries.level_increase: The Gotal are sending in reinforcements!
entries.quest_destroy_d: Engage and eliminate all elite starfighter pilots of the Gotal bandit clan. This will teach them respect for the Rodians!
entries.quest_location_d: The Kashyyyk system is loaded with ill-tempered, disrespectful Gotal Bandits. Seek them out! Destroy them all!
entries.targets_behind: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer: pcontrast3 Hostile fighters coming in from behind you.
entries.targets_detected: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer: pcontrast3 Scans indicate hostile fighters on attack vector!
entries.taunt_1: The Rodians can't be paying you enough for this! Give up!
entries.taunt_2: You think the Rodians are your friends? You're crazy!
entries.taunt_3: This doesn't have to involve you, mercenary!
entries.taunt_4: You should quit before this gets ugly!
entries.taunt_5: Make it easy on yourself. Hyperspace to another system!
entries.title: Rodian Protectors: Seek and Destroy Gotal Bandits
entries.title_d: The Rodians have taken an interest in you now that you are a veteran Civilian Protector. The Gotal have offended the Rodian Warlord Sordaan by hunting in his hunting grounds without permission. This is unacceptable. Smash the Gotal Bandits fleet. Teach them respect!
